OL,5, A man has admitted keeping his former  
OL,6, flatmate's body in a freezer for nearly
OL,7, two years but denied using his bank    
OL,8, card to obtain cash.                   
OL,10,FJohn Wainwright, 71, died in September 
OL,11,F2018 and was discovered in August 2020.
OL,13,FDamion Johnson pleaded guilty at Derby 
OL,14,FCrown Court to keeping the body in the 
OL,15,Ffreezer of a property in Birmingham.   
OL,17,FThe offence is believed to have taken  
OL,18,Fplace when the pair lived in a flat in 
OL,19,Fthe city centre. Mr Wainwright's cause 
OL,20,Fof death is yet to be ascertained.     
